com.EventBus

Annotation Type Subscribe


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface Subscribe
    Marks a method as an event subscriber.

    The type of subscribed event will be indicated by the method's first (and only) parameter in this framework
